data.title: 输出什么？
data.options: {"options":["Woah some cool data","Oh finally!","Woah some cool data Oh finally!","Oops didn't work Oh finally!"],"isMulti":false,"answer":[2]}
data.explanation: 在 `try` 块区，我们打印 `myPromise` 变量的 awaited 值： `"Woah some cool data"`。因为`try` 块区没有错误抛出，`catch` 块区的代码并不执行。`finally` 块区的代码 _总是_ 执行，`"Oh finally!"` 被输出。
